name: Chicago flag bandana - WHITE
description: This listing is for (1) white Chicago flag bandana. Each bandana has two print locations so they can be worn multiple ways to display Chicago's stars and stripes! Wear it as a headband, around your neck, over your head, etc! The black bandana is printed exactly the same. The bandanas are washing machine-friendly. Machine or line dry and wear them to the next festival/concert/sporting event/everywhere! Additional photos can be found on our Facebook page: Facebook.com/illstateclothing *Products are shipped First Class (3-7 days) by default. If you'd like Priority Shipping (2-3 days) select 'Albania' as your country during checkout and the shipping costs will reflect the difference.

name: EDC Chicago tank top
description: We came, we raved, we loved. The inaugural EDC Chicago is now behind us. It was a cold, wet, muddy, and phenomenal weekend. We had a blast and received excellent feedback on these tank tops so we decided to make more! This design pays homage to the official/ unofficial/ not-Joliet host of EDC Chicago. Printed on purple unisex American Apparel tank tops and available in sizes Small, Medium, Large, and XL Additional photos can be found on our Facebook page: Facebook.com/illstateclothing *Products are shipped First Class (3-7 days) by default. If you'd like Priority Shipping (2-3 days) select 'Albania' as your country during checkout and the shipping costs will reflect the difference.
